name: Тethег
description: Tether (USDT) is a blockchain-based stablecoin pegged 1:1 to the U.S. Dollar. Issued by Tether Limited, USDT maintains full fiat reserves and enables seamless transfers of digital dollars across blockchains. On Solana, USDT offers fast, low-fee transactions and serves as a key liquidity asset in DeFi, trading, and payment systems.
